            "heading": "Make a Gift",
            "body": "<p>Thank you for your support!</p><p>To make a gift with a credit card, please fill out the secure form below.</p><p>A Donor-Advised Fund allows you to recommend grants to the Museum directly from your charitable giving account. Please notify The Aldrich if you make a DAF gift as the sponsoring organization may not share your information. To recommend a grant, contact your DAF provider and direct it to:<br/>The Aldrich Contemporary Art Museum<br/>Tax ID: 06-6069965</p><p>If you wish to make a gift of stock or to send a wire transfer, please contact Kris Honeycutt, Director of Development, at 203.403.7364 or <a href=\"mailto:khoneycutt@thealdrich.org\">khoneycutt@thealdrich.org</a>.</p>",
